snippet: The departure of the United Nations peacekeeping mission is a significant milestone in East Timor’s journey after its independence from Indonesia in 1999.
abstract: United Nations ends peacekeeping mission in East Timor; formal end of deployment is  significant milestone in country’s journey after its independence from Indonesia in 1999.
lead_paragraph: The departure of the United Nations peacekeeping mission is a significant milestone in East Timor’s journey after its independence from Indonesia in 1999.

headline.seo: In East Timor, U.N. Ends Peacekeeping Role
